author: kdy1
message:
fix(next-swc): Apply SWC minifier bugfixes (#81098)

### What?

Update `swc_core` to `v29.4.2` 

### Why?

To apply https://github.com/swc-project/swc/pull/10740 and https://github.com/swc-project/swc/pull/10741
